The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 Blair son to work as intern

 London, Jan. 13 (Reuters): British Prime Minister Tony Blairs eldest son Euan is to gain work experience as an intern with financial public relations company Finsbury, people familiar with the matter said today.

 Blair, who turns 22 on January 19, is to spend two weeks with the agency taking part in meetings and gaining an overview of how the communications business works, one of the sources said. 




